<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
    body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #FFEB3B;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url('https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/03/21/48/06/360_F_321480639_mVJIrZLLOH0pEd00Bo2vw1LA3k8IpnjR.jpg');
            background-repeat: repeat;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #F44336;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .nav-links ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .nav-links li {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }


        .navbar.active {
            width: 400px; 
        }

        .dropdown-details {
        position: relative;
        }

        .dropdown-details .dropdown-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        position: absolute;
        top: 100%;
        left: 0;
        background-color: #ef5b50;
        box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 10px;
        }

        .dropdown-details .dropdown-item {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .dropdown-details a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .dropdown-details a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .hero {
            background-color: #2196F3;  
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .btn {
            background-color: #4CAF50; 
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;  
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #388E3C; 
        }
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #E0E0E0;
            border: 1px solid #BDBDBD;  
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .card img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .dropdown {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .dropdown-content {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: #E0E0E0;  
            min-width: 160px;
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            z-index: 1;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .dropdown:hover .dropdown-content {
            display: block;
        }
        .dropdown button {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            outline: none;
            color: #fff;
        }
        
    </style>
    <title>About Lego Collection</title>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: '/'}) %>
     
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>About Lego Fantasia</h1>
            <p>All about the amazing world of Legos and the passion behind it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;">
            <img src="https://educationsnapshots.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2022/01/seneca-college-newnham-campus-food-hall-3-700x467-compact.jpg" alt="Harsh Patel" style="border-radius: 8px; max-width: 100%;">
            <div style="background-color: #e4ed36; color: darkblue; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
                <h2>Harsh Patel</h2>
                <p>
                    I am Harsh Patel, enrolled in the CPP program of Seneca College. Currently, I'm studying 4 courses: Web322, OOP345, SYD211, NAT161, and DBS311. I'm deeply passionate about Lego and aim to blend my academic knowledge with my love for these unique building blocks.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
